products.description: 10th Gen Intel Core i9-10900K unlocked desktop processor. Featuring Intel Turbo Boost Max Technology 3. 0, unlocked 10th Gen Intel Core desktop processors are optimized for enthusiast gamers and serious creators and help deliver high performance overclocking for an added boost. Thermal solution NOT included in the box. ONLY compatible with 400 series chipset based motherboard. 125W.
